title: My Tip Sheet for Week 2
text:
Tips:
How to make new blog post:

open blog in Rstudio, find posts folder, copy post and save as new post name

How to commit and push changes to github:

make change, render website via Rstudio, commit in github desktop w/ commit msg, push to github.com
